title: Tibet - Wikileaks China-censored protest - March 14-17 2008
description:
"Tibet - Wikileaks China-censored protest - March 14-17 2008" is a Wikileaks.be archive of photos (some very gory) and videos of the March 14-17 Tibetan protest against Chinese rule and "ethnic-cleansing" of native Tibetans from their own country. This material is censored by China. China has also recently severed internet traffic to and from Tibet.

Use 7zip File Archiver (from 7-zip.org) to open archives.

See also: TIBET CRY OF THE SNOW LION 2002 DVD9 full rip to 2DVD5 lossless

And: Nine Commentaries on the Communist Party China [english] 2005-2007 XviD
